IN: mongodb.tuple.state

<PRIVATE

CONSTANT: MDB_TUPLE_INFO       "_mfd_t_info"

PRIVATE>

: <tuple-info> ( tuple -- tuple-info )
    class [ V{ } clone ] dip over
    [ [ name>> ] dip push ]
    [ [ vocabulary>> ] dip push ] 2bi ; inline

: tuple-info ( assoc -- tuple-info )
